<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 04:09:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列和真主党跨境贸易冲击；以色列国防军称两名士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/israel-and-hezbollah-trade-blows-across-border-idf-says-two-soldiers-injured/00000190-d303-dbb4-a7d2-db0f14160000</link><description>以色列军方表示，有 40 枚火箭弹和无人机越过边境发射，造成两名士兵受伤并引发火灾。黎巴嫩报道称，以色列国防军袭击了真主党军火库和一辆车辆，造成至少四名平民受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 02:33:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/israel-and-hezbollah-trade-blows-across-border-idf-says-two-soldiers-injured/00000190-d303-dbb4-a7d2-db0f14160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队拦截从也门向以色列南部埃拉特发射的导弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article-live/fires-rage-in-northern-israel-after-rocket-fire-sources-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets/00000190-d2bb-dd40-ab95-f6bbc5be0000</link><description>以色列袭击也门胡塞武装港口，胡塞武装称三人死亡、87 人受伤 ■ 以色列国防军称，超过 40 枚火箭弹从黎巴嫩发射到以色列北部；军队称，两名士兵在无人机袭击中受伤 ■ 以色列国防军：战斗机袭击了加沙恐怖组织用来储存资金的建筑 ■ 沙特阿拉伯表示没有参与以色列对也门的袭击</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 00:56:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article-live/fires-rage-in-northern-israel-after-rocket-fire-sources-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets/00000190-d2bb-dd40-ab95-f6bbc5be0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院关于以色列占领的裁决的执行取决于联合国和美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/implementation-of-icj-ruling-on-israeli-occupation-depends-on-the-un-and-u-s/00000190-d1d0-dd40-ab95-f7dbe2710000</link><description>国际法院正式表示，以色列对约旦河西岸的占领是“非法的”，必须予以拆除。这项裁决虽然不具有约束力，但却给以色列带来了压力，并可能改变现实，但以色列的盟友和国际社会需要认真对待它</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 00:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/implementation-of-icj-ruling-on-israeli-occupation-depends-on-the-un-and-u-s/00000190-d1d0-dd40-ab95-f7dbe2710000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列对也门的首次袭击，战争在九个月后出现了危险的新转折</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/with-israels-first-ever-attack-in-yemen-the-war-takes-a-dangerous-new-turn/00000190-d1ce-dd02-a3d3-fbdff1850000</link><description>这次袭击的成功——距离以色列约 1,700 公里——向整个地区，特别是伊朗传达了以色列远程军事能力的信息。这次袭击以及周末的其他新闻给内塔尼亚胡总理本已备受争议的美国之行带来了更多负担</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 22:39:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/with-israels-first-ever-attack-in-yemen-the-war-takes-a-dangerous-new-turn/00000190-d1ce-dd02-a3d3-fbdff1850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在特拉维夫无人机致命袭击后袭击也门；胡塞武装誓言做出回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-20/ty-article/israel-attacks-yemen-following-fatal-tel-aviv-drone-strike-houthis-vow-to-respond/00000190-d10d-d5cb-a59c-fd4f1ea80000</link><description>胡塞武装报告称，此次袭击造成 3 人死亡、87 人受伤，炼油厂和电力基础设施受损。周五，一架从也门发射的无人机在特拉维夫爆炸，造成一人死亡、八人受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 20:06:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-20/ty-article/israel-attacks-yemen-following-fatal-tel-aviv-drone-strike-houthis-vow-to-respond/00000190-d10d-d5cb-a59c-fd4f1ea80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事，第 288 天：以色列国防军袭击也门；黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射了 40 枚火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-288-israel-strikes-in-yemen-40-rockets-from-lebanon-launched-at-north/00000190-d156-dc8b-a1dd-d9f70c890000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，在胡塞武装无人机袭击特拉维夫一天后，以色列袭击了胡塞武装控制的也门荷台达港，造成一人死亡 ■ 黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射了 40 多枚火箭弹 ■ 据报道，至少 30 人死亡以色列袭击加沙拉法 ■ 《纽约时报》报道称，拜登不会在总理内塔尼亚胡下周访问华盛顿之前退出总统竞选</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 18:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-288-israel-strikes-in-yemen-40-rockets-from-lebanon-launched-at-north/00000190-d156-dc8b-a1dd-d9f70c890000</guid></item><item><title>随着内塔尼亚胡前往美国，以色列人开始了为期一周的人质协议和反对政府抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-20/ty-article/.premium/israelis-open-week-of-protests-for-hostage-deal-against-govt-as-netanyahu-heads-to-u-s/00000190-d058-dbb4-a7d2-db5f671e0000</link><description>周六，以色列各地数十个地点发生了示威活动，有报道称谈判取得了进展。未来一周，人质亲属计划跟随内塔尼亚胡总理访问美国，并在他计划向国会发表讲话期间举行大规模集会</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 15:01:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-20/ty-article/.premium/israelis-open-week-of-protests-for-hostage-deal-against-govt-as-netanyahu-heads-to-u-s/00000190-d058-dbb4-a7d2-db5f671e0000</guid></item><item><title>两名巴勒斯坦人在西岸暴力冲突中被定居者打伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-20/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-wounded-by-settlers-in-west-bank-amid-violent-clashes/00000190-cfd0-d89a-a1f7-ffd00eb40000</link><description>一名以色列定居者还在哈瓦拉枪杀了一名巴勒斯坦男子，几名定居者放火焚烧了同一地区的橄榄园并损坏了一辆救护车</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 11:54:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-20/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-wounded-by-settlers-in-west-bank-amid-violent-clashes/00000190-cfd0-d89a-a1f7-ffd00eb40000</guid></item><item><title>芝加哥犹太人如何帮助德鲁兹青年在以色列争取更美好的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-chicago-jews-are-helping-druze-youth-fight-for-a-better-future-in-israel/00000190-c58e-d2f8-abdb-e5eed5a50000</link><description>一项新计划旨在增强以色列德鲁兹人的权力并培养他们的领导力，并解决该社区面临的一些问题。该倡议诞生于伊利诺伊州</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 08:58:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-chicago-jews-are-helping-druze-youth-fight-for-a-better-future-in-israel/00000190-c58e-d2f8-abdb-e5eed5a50000</guid></i