</item><item><title>50 岁男子被确认为特拉维夫无人机袭击的受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/50-year-old-man-identified-as-victim-of-tel-aviv-drone-attack/00000190-ccb9-d89a-a1f7-feb960130000</link><description>来自特拉维夫的叶夫根尼·费德 (Evgeny Ferder) 在可能从也门发动的突然袭击中丧生，另有八人受伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 20:57:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/50-year-old-man-identified-as-victim-of-tel-aviv-drone-attack/00000190-ccb9-d89a-a1f7-feb960130000</guid></item><item><title>一名巴勒斯坦男孩在结束足球训练回家的路上被以色列军队枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-palestinian-boy-was-on-his-way-home-form-soccer-when-he-was-shot-dead-by-israeli-troops/00000190-cca4-dbaa-af9c-fcafea620000</link><description>士兵们开枪打伤了一名来自拉马拉的 12 岁男孩，并在 20 分钟内阻止了一辆巴勒斯坦救护车将他疏散。被遗弃在路边流血八天后去世</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 20:39:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-palestinian-boy-was-on-his-way-home-form-soccer-when-he-was-shot-dead-by-israeli-troops/00000190-cca4-dbaa-af9c-fcafea620000</guid></item><item><title>以色列激进反犹太复国主义组织的退伍军人现在相信什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-the-veterans-of-a-radical-israeli-anti-zionist-group-believe-now/00000190-caa3-d258-a3ff-eeab59dd0000</link><description>50 年前，对于以色列公众来说，Matzpen 组织的退伍军人过于激进，现在他们正在参加一场关于控制阿拉伯人口 18 年的军政府的戏剧。这次重聚对他们来说是一个重新评估的机会——有些人感到悔恨，有些人感到平反</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 19:56:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-the-veterans-of-a-radical-israeli-anti-zionist-group-believe-now/00000190-caa3-d258-a3ff-eeab59dd0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院刚刚拆除了以色列占领的主要防御设施之一</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/the-icj-just-demolished-one-of-israels-key-defenses-of-the-occupation/00000190-cc54-dcff-afd4-cfdc29ee0000</link><description>海牙国际法院不遗余力地认定以色列剥夺巴勒斯坦人的吞并主义政策违反了国际法的主要原则。问题是接下来会发生什么</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 19:44:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/the-icj-just-demolished-one-of-israels-key-defenses-of-the-occupation/00000190-cc54-dcff-afd4-cfdc29ee0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院关于占领的决定超出了以色列最担心的范围</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/icjs-decision-on-the-occupation-goes-beyond-israels-worst-fears/00000190-cbe6-dc8b-a1dd-cbe7a2350000</link><description>国际法院的咨询意见削弱了以色列关于长期占领约旦河西岸和加沙地带的基本论点，该意见实质上为各国、机构和企业提供了惩罚以色列的理由。忽略它不应该是一个选择</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 18:36:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/icjs-decision-on-the-occupation-goes-beyond-israels-worst-fears/00000190-cbe6-dc8b-a1dd-cbe7a2350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列交战，第 287 天：胡塞武装无人机杀死以色列人；国际法院对以色列占领作出裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-287-houthi-drone-kills-israeli-icj-rules-on-israeli-occupation/00000190-cbe0-d5cb-a59c-efef02b40000</link><description>胡塞武装无人机袭击在特拉维夫造成以色列平民死亡、八人受伤 ■ 国际法院：以色列对约旦河西岸和东耶路撒冷的占领是“事实上的吞并”，以色列定居点违反国际法 ■ 以色列国防军：越来越多的迹象表明哈马斯军事首领穆罕默德·戴夫在上周的空袭中丧生 ■ 战争进入 287 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 17:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-287-houthi-drone-kills-israeli-icj-rules-on-israeli-occupation/00000190-cbe0-d5cb-a59c-efef02b40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列领导人对国际法院的“反犹太主义”裁决感到愤怒，巴勒斯坦总统表示正义已经胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/as-israeli-leaders-seethe-at-antisemitic-icj-palestinian-president-says-justice-has-won/00000190-cb67-decf-a7b2-dff7f2240000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡：犹太人“不占领自己的土地” ■ 拉皮德：裁决“受到反犹太主义的玷污”，只为“伊斯兰恐怖主义”服务 ■ 本·格维尔、斯莫特里奇：吞并约旦河西岸的时间到了 ■ 蒂比：国际法院“准确地捕捉到了现实” ” ■ 巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯：“正义的胜利”</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 16:28:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/as-israeli-leaders-seethe-at-antisemitic-icj-palestinian-president-says-justice-has-won/00000190-cb67-decf-a7b2-dff7f2240000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院称以色列占领巴勒斯坦领土“非法”，必须停止存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/world-court-israeli-occupation-of-palestinian-territories-unlawful-must-end-presence/00000190-cb67-dbb4-a7d2-db6fabec0000</link><description>世界法院称以色列一直在实施种族隔离，应就其对约旦河西岸和东耶路撒冷的占领做出赔偿</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 15:33:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-19/ty-article/.premium/world-court-israeli-occupation-of-palestinian-territories-unlawful-must-end-presence/00000190-cb67-dbb4-a7d2-db6fabec0000</guid></item></channel></rss>